                        in Home Security Detroit?</h3>
                </div>

                <p class="text-[#58585B] text-sm leading-6 w-full md:w-[65%] " >
                    Since Detroit is one of the most dangerous cities in America, there are a few things you should make sure you’re getting in your home security package. Here’s what you need: HD Security cameras, Door and window motion sensors, Remote monitoring, Monitoring cameras with cloud back-up, Wireless connection, Easy installation process, Motion sensors, Night vision. These features will help to give you better overall protection around the clock. For example, with HD quality monitoring cameras, you will be able to see better what is happening in and around your house. You never want to be caught after a burglary without clear footage of what happened. Having HD cameras will help you to identify better who was at home and help you better protect yourself in the future. The other features on the list do similar things. They will help you to stay safe by protecting your family and your home.
                </p>

